## 2. Design & UI Rules

### POXY Aesthetic — Dark Cyber-Luxury
POXY is dark, immersive, and cryptographic. Think: underground digital vault meets
neo-brutalist collector's world. NOT generic SaaS. NOT purple gradients on white.

**Color Palette (CSS variables — always use these):**
```css
--poxy-bg: #0a0a0f;          /* near-black base */
--poxy-surface: #111118;     /* card surfaces */
--poxy-border: #1e1e2e;      /* subtle borders */
--poxy-accent: #00f5a0;      /* neon mint — primary accent */
--poxy-accent-2: #7c3aed;    /* deep violet — secondary */
--poxy-accent-3: #f59e0b;    /* amber — legendary/rare glow */
--poxy-text: #e2e8f0;        /* primary text */
--poxy-muted: #64748b;       /* muted/secondary text */
--poxy-danger: #ef4444;      /* burn/danger actions */
```

**Rarity Glow Colors:**
```css
--rarity-common: #94a3b8;
--rarity-uncommon: #22c55e;
--rarity-rare: #3b82f6;
--rarity-epic: #a855f7;
--rarity-legendary: #f59e0b;
--rarity-mythic: #ec4899;
--rarity-secret: #ffffff;
```

### Typography
- Display/headings: `'Syne'` or `'Bricolage Grotesque'` (Google Fonts) — bold, geometric
- Body/UI: `'DM Mono'` or `'IBM Plex Mono'` for crypto/data elements
- Secondary body: `'Plus Jakarta Sans'` for readable prose
- NEVER use: Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui as primary fonts
- Font sizes: mobile-first, minimum 14px for body, 11px for labels

### Animations
- Entry animations: staggered reveals with `animation-delay` (50ms increments)
- Rarity reveals: scale + glow pulse — legendary/mythic get dramatic entrance
- Hover states: subtle lift (`translateY(-2px)`) + border glow
- Page transitions: fade + slight upward drift (200ms ease-out)
- Lootbox opening: multi-stage — suspense build → flash → reveal
- Performance mode toggle exists — respect it (reduce/remove animations when active)
- NO animations that block interaction or cause layout shift

### Layout
- Mobile-first always — design for 375px, enhance for larger screens
- Bottom navigation bar is sacred — never move or restructure it
- Cards: rounded-xl (16px), dark surface, subtle border, glow on hover
- Modals: full-screen on mobile, centered max-width on desktop
- Spacing: 8px base unit — use multiples (8, 16, 24, 32, 48)
- Safe areas: account for iOS notch/home bar (`env(safe-area-inset-*)`)

### Component Patterns
- Buttons: primary = accent fill + dark text; secondary = border only; danger = red
- Inputs: dark background, accent border on focus, monospace font for hashes
- Badges/chips: small, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.05em
- Loading states: pulsing skeleton or spinner — never blank white flash
- Empty states: always have icon + message + action CTA

